		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64679476"><p>If by "drastically reduced" you mean "achieve net negative through green power generation and artificial sequestration", then I agree.</p><p>Nature sequesters carbon far too slowly for our needs, we're going to have to put it back in the ground ourselves or as far as anyone alive today is concerned, today's CO2 levels are the new normal for the rest of time.  (Most likely longer than humans have had anything we'd recognize as 'civilization')</p></div>
